data.description: Open Saturday December  16th from 12-2. Well maintained brick ranch in Garden City. Close to transportation, shopping, city services, and all other amenities. Kitchen remodeled with cherry cabinetry and granite counter. All stainless steel appliances to say and microwave is being replaced. Main bath has been remodeled with a custom tiled walk-in shower. Hardwood floors on main floor except for the kitchen and bathroom.  Doorwall from back bedroom to a nice deck that has a retractable awning. Nice backyard and 2 1/2 car detached garage with power and heat and a shed for additional storage. Second refrigerator in garage will stay. Full finished basement has an electric fireplace and half bath.  Brand New Hot water Heater Nov 2023. Large laundry area with washer and dryer to stay. Newer windows throughout. Seller will provide Certificate of Occupancy at closing.  Roof certification letter will be needed from the buyer. So many lovely features in this home.  Take a look! You will not be disappointed. Easy to show.
